  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1951 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The framed leaflet features a photograph of a couple in uniforms. They are wearing similar peaked caps. The woman is wearing a jacket; the man is dressed in a coat. He has a scar under his left ear. He is clutching her right upper arm with his left hand. He is taller than she is. He is looking down at her; she is looking up at him. Both are smiling. The Serbo-Croatian translation of the original English film title, ‘Force of arms’, is printed across the bottom of the image: ‘Snaga oružja’.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The movie was directed by Michael Curtiz and released in 1951.</ab>
